<text top="77" left="83" width="325" height="54" font="1">Learning Goals</text>
<text top="150" left="49" width="596" height="35" font="2">What are the core principles of UK GDPR?</text>
<text top="225" left="49" width="1002" height="35" font="2">What are the rights of the subjects of data gathering activities under the </text>
<text top="263" left="49" width="108" height="35" font="2">GDPR?</text>
<text top="339" left="49" width="920" height="35" font="2">What are the implications of the Data Protection Act for Computer </text>
<text top="377" left="49" width="323" height="35" font="2">Scientists in particular?</text>
<text top="452" left="49" width="844" height="35" font="2">What is Privacy Shield and why do we need to care about it?</text>
</page>
