<text top="78" left="83" width="455" height="54" font="1">(and maybe the UK?)</text>
<text top="145" left="58" width="955" height="40" font="9">GDPR provisions on transference of data to non EU country</text>
<text top="188" left="58" width="914" height="40" font="9">- Allowed to countries with adequate protection regimes </text>
<text top="231" left="98" width="250" height="40" font="9">(very small list!)</text>
<text top="274" left="58" width="794" height="40" font="9">- Allowed to countries with adequate contractual </text>
