<text top="361" left="98" width="428" height="40" font="9">country which is hard to do</text>
<text top="447" left="58" width="991" height="40" font="9">Allowed to countries with something like the US “<i>safe harbour </i></text>
<text top="490" left="58" width="138" height="40" font="11"><i>scheme</i>”</text>
<text top="534" left="58" width="511" height="40" font="9">- Many issues with this though!</text>
