<text top="300" left="58" width="903" height="40" font="9">An Austrian privacy campaigner challenged that decision</text>
<text top="343" left="58" width="683" height="40" font="9">• In part citing the Edward Snowden leaks</text>
<text top="411" left="131" width="835" height="40" font="11"><i>The EU court found the protections were inadequate</i></text>
<text top="483" left="58" width="871" height="40" font="9">The new scheme is more stringent, the Privacy-Shield </text>
